info.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 04 at 9:09AM PST until January 05 at 10:00AM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM PST FRIDAY... ...HIGH WIND WARNING IS CANCELLED... * WHAT...North winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 to 55 mph. * WHERE...Santa Ynez Mountains Eastern Range, Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains, Southern Ventura County Mountains and Interstate 5 Corridor. * WHEN...Until 10 AM PST Friday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
